tell him you love him,

22:21.820 --> 22:23.270
maybe tell him how much
you're proud of him...

22:23.320 --> 22:27.380
Stop fucking picking at me, Robert.

22:31.330 --> 22:33.520
Please go.

22:57.690 --> 22:59.840
You okay?

22:59.890 --> 23:02.410
Yeah, fine.

23:03.660 --> 23:05.750
