Oh, God. Hey.

31:51.920 --> 31:52.870
Aw, Jesus.

31:52.920 --> 31:55.510
Hey! Hey, KD.

31:55.560 --> 31:56.640
Hey.

31:56.690 --> 31:59.050
Hey.

31:59.100 --> 32:01.080
